review_data.title: Smood delivery service is terrible
review_data.content: Smood delivery service is terrible. They promised to deliver in one hour. Hour has gone by and no one even picked up the food. To add insult to injury the phone hotline which one is charged for just puts you on hold. Lousy lousy lousy
